folder: Van Sicklen St. & Glenmore Ave., Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Van Sicklen St. - Glenmore Ave.
text:
Van Siclen Avenue, adjoining the S. E. corner of Glenmore Avenue, showing the East End Baptist Church. View 2 shows also the corner house.

September 14, 1940
Views 1,2

P. L. Sperr
